+# Decision Workspace
+
+Put your ROS2 decision-making packages under `src/`.
+
+Inside the `decision-dev` container, source the stack overlay first:
+
+```bash
+source /opt/ros/humble/setup.bash
+source /opt/ros2_ws/install/setup.bash
+```
+
+Then build your own workspace with:
+
+```bash
+cd /workspace/decision_ws
+colcon build --merge-install
+source install/setup.bash
+```
